                     <interp inst="t18240916-247-person2068" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I <rs id="t18240916-247-viclabel1319" type="occupation">keep the Turk's-head</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-247-victim2064 t18240916-247-viclabel1319"></join>, Harley-street; this woman was brought to my house; I had seen her about the neighbourhood before, but she had not been at my house that day; I do not know where she had taken my pot from; I believe it had been sent out with some ale at noon.</p>
